    shortAnswer: `Audit your sales pipeline by checking every open deal for four things: correct stage, a dated next step, a defensible close date, and recent buyer activity. Close-lost the zombies, correct the mis-staged deals, and recalculate coverage. A clean audit turns a fantasy forecast into a real one.`,
