    shortAnswer: `Nurture leads by segmenting them by fit and stage, delivering relevant value on a steady cadence across email and other channels, tracking engagement, and handing off to sales the moment a lead crosses your intent threshold. The goal is to stay useful until timing is right, not to blast everyone the same message.`,
