    shortAnswer: `Generate more leads by knowing your ICP, then running a measured mix of inbound content, outbound sequences to a target account list, referrals, and partnerships. Track cost and conversion per channel, double down on what produces qualified opportunities, and follow up fast so the leads you get actually convert.`,
