    shortAnswer: `Calculate sales velocity by multiplying the number of opportunities by average deal value and win rate, then dividing by the average sales cycle length in days. The result is revenue generated per day. Improving any of the first three levers or shortening the cycle increases how fast your pipeline produces revenue.`,
