    shortAnswer: `Calculate quota attainment by dividing a rep's actual closed results by their quota for the period and multiplying by 100. For example, 220,000 dollars closed against a 200,000 dollar quota is 110 percent attainment. Look at the distribution across the team, not just the average, to judge whether quotas are set right.`,
