    shortAnswer: `Improve forecast accuracy by cleaning the pipeline, requiring close dates tied to buyer-confirmed events, using consistent stage exit criteria, measuring accuracy by rep to expose bias, and blending rep judgment with historical conversion. Coach sandbaggers and happy-ears reps differently, and snapshot forecasts so you can learn from every miss.`,
