    shortAnswer: `Build a territory plan by defining how you segment the market (geography, industry, segment, or named accounts), scoring each territory's potential, balancing them so reps have fair and equal opportunity, assigning accounts clearly to avoid conflicts, and reviewing coverage against capacity. Rebalance as the market and headcount change.`,
